{"tid":2171640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"瓏門冰室 定期考核","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T10:58:09.000Z","uid":244394,"like":121,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0b59cffa7788b34e0b82aee03eee04b19c738a26","tid":2171640,"uid":244394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6Z0UkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6Z0UkV.jpg&h=f429642a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2E9Uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2E9Uv.jpg&h=07a922ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日試芝士焗飯 我覺得係合格仲有啲好食既<br />\n個芝士汁有芝士味又夠汁 食得出用左幾款不同既芝士有不同口感 <br />\n飯底有炒底 但有少少唔夠乾身 <br />\n雞扒係正常茶記雞<br />\n奶茶就仲係有少少澀同鞋<br />\n<br />\n不過真係進步左希望下次考核會再有所提升"},{"pid":"6be54024e47b25efb5f80b2f10ef621a2eda709b","tid":2171640,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85690f0038d63f7ae4320baef2b4e03460ea6425","tid":2171640,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8695438166f4914890a0ea27d58522c13d7ca091","tid":2171640,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a410a2851ad897cebceec3cc57fad6316a14eca6","tid":2171640,"uid":1024,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"想試 好似幾好食<br />\n但65蚊...好似食其他仲抵.."},{"pid":"33cf2740d43ba333615e0d86272d825f914578e3","tid":2171640,"uid":102